  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bae\u0bb4\u0bc8 : \u0bb0\u0bca\u0b9a\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2 \u0baa\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bae\u0bcd - 21 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Rain with strong winds in the hills: Floods in Rosalla area - 21 families affected",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Heavy rain and strong winds are blowing in the hilly areas since the morning of 03rd.",
        "Due to the incessant heavy rains, floods and small landslides have occurred in various areas.",
        "Agricultural lands and residences of plantation workers have also been affected due to flood water in Rosalla Aitri area under Vattawela police division.",
        "Due to the rain, 21 houses in the area were filled with flood water and few more houses were inundated.",
        "The victims said that if the water level in the Aitri river, which supplies water to the Kalapoda river near the house, rises, the flood water enters the house.",
        "The victims mentioned that not a single room in their house was covered in flood water, and many items such as items kept in their cupboards and household appliances were damaged in the flood water.",
        "Arrangements have been made to accommodate more than 60 people from 25 affected families in relatives' houses, neighbors' houses, and in the Viharai in the garden.",
        "Meanwhile, the Gramsevakar of the area has visited the victims and the incident has been brought to the attention of the Ambakamuwa Divisional Secretariat and the officials of the District Inter-Management Center."
      ],
